title: Prosecutors seek 30 year jail term for South Korean ex-president
text:
Prosecutors seek 30 year jail term for South Korean ex-president 8:54am EST - 01:06 
South Korean prosecutors seek a 30-year jail term for former President Park Geun-hye who was ousted last year amid an influence-peddling scandal that rocked the country’s business and political elite. Grace Lee reports.
